fg_segments: Privacy Policyupdated on December 31st 2018While visiting this website, information recorded in small files called "cookies" are installed on your computer or mobile device.
Some of these cookies are first-party cookies, necessary for the functioning of this website.
Other cookies are third-party social-sharing and advertising-related cookies.The social-sharing cookies may temporarily store an IP address and set a client cookie for security purposes.

Outside the EEA (European Economic Area), the advertising-related cookies collect information about your IP address, as well as the type of browser and operating system you're using, in order to provide advertisements about goods and services of interest to you based on your prior visits to this or other websites.
For more information, see https://www.google.com/policies/technologies/ads.You may at any time opt out of personalized advertising here.

Within the EEA, all advertisements are non-personalized. However, they do use cookies to allow for frequency capping (a feature that limits the number of times ads appear to the same person), aggregated ad reporting (a feature that measures ad performance), and to combat fraud and abuse.
You may at any time opt out of personalized advertising here.
You may at any time choose to refuse cookies through your browser:Disneyclips.com is not responsible for the content or privacy policies of websites visited through external links.
You should always check the privacy policies and terms of use of any website or service before providing personal information.
Please be advised that this privacy policy may be changed in the future. Return to see any changes made.
